definition: denoting a quantity consisting of six items or units, a playing card or domino or die whose upward face shows six pips
details:
adjective
- denoting a quantity consisting of six items or units
= synonyms: half dozen, half-dozen
noun
- a playing card or domino or die whose upward face shows six pips
= synonyms: six-spot
- the cardinal number that is the sum of five and one
= synonyms: sestet, sextet, sixer, sise, half a dozen, sextuplet, hexad
